metadata.description: SweetNFTreat: Birthday Cupcakes is a batch of 7,777 delicious digital collectibles on an ERC721A contract. They're meant to be minted to other people's wallets as digital, collectible greetings. (But you can also mint them for yourself if you just want to collect them.) Some are rarer than others, some are legendary, and all are super tasty (mixing 300+ different "ingredient" traits). There will be two much smaller greeting card sets (1,111 each) using these same cupcake traits. Those sets will have different messages and will not repeat the same trait combos in this 7,777 set. Thus, over three collections, there will be 9,999 unique cupcakes in the overall series. All brought to you by NFTGreetings.xyz (the digitial greeting card arm of GenerativeNFTs.io. Want to do your own line of digital greeting cards? Give us a shout!) And hey ... Happy Birthday!
metadata.name: SweetNFTreat: Birthday Cupcake #1
